只是使她更重要的任务更加重要。</p><p> Lipa目前的澳大利亚巡回演唱会支持她的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">激进的乐观</a>》，并在本月的墨尔本上一场演出中，她还报道了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-covers-aussie-legend-kylie-minogues-cant-get-you-out-of-my-head-in-melbourne-3847894">Kylie Minogue&#39;s的“ Cother Cable Bave You Lats My Heard”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-natalie-imbruglias-torn-during-second-melbourne-concert-3847685">Natalie Imbruglia的“ Torn torn”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-ac-dcs-highway-to-hell-in-melbourne-3847044">AC/DC的“ Highway to Hell”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3848472" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3848472" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3848472" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dua_lipa_troye-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3848472" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa和Troye Sivan于2025年3月22日在澳大利亚墨尔本举行的Rod Laver Arena。 （Naomi Rahim/Getty Images的照片）</figcaption></figure><p>在澳大利亚结束后，Lipa将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-adds-uk-europe-australia-and-north-america-dates-to-2025-radical-optimism-tour-3793188">今年夏天前往英国进行更多的现场表演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-unveils-details-of-huge-wembley-show-in-2025-3771131">在伦敦的温布利体育场（6月20日，21日）举行了两场巨大的音乐会，</a>